   <refnamediv>
      <refname>ml:adhoc-query</refname>
      <refpurpose>Run an adhoc query on MarkLogic Server</refpurpose>
   </refnamediv>
   <refsynopsisdiv>
      <xi:include href="../declarations.xml" xpointer="xpath(/*/*[@type='ml:adhoc-query'])"/>
   </refsynopsisdiv>
   <refsection>
      <title>Description</title>

<para>The <tag>ml:adhoc-query</tag> step performs an adhoc query on a 
<link xlink:href="http://www.marklogic.com">Mark Logic</link> Server.
</para>

<para>To use this step you must have a Mark Logic Server and the
<link xlink:href="http://xqzone.marklogic.com/download/default.xqy#XCC">Java
XCC</link> libraries.</para>

   </refsection>
